{"tid":1007290,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"夾餸比人呢樣野真係垃圾中既垃圾文化","createTime":"2019-02-03T16:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T16:41:54.000Z","uid":24615,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6d902bdbc9f0c00bac13003992d0920e87cb3fa4","tid":1007290,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"特別係d唔熟既親戚 <br />\n完全唔知你既喜好又唔知你有咩唔食得<br />\n<br />\n一副懶係關心後輩既樣<br />\n<br />\n見你成晚唔食果樣就偏要問你「做咩唔食xxx ar?」然後就夾比你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你拒絕話唔鍾意/唔食得 佢又黑晒面覺得你落佢面<br />\n<br />\n放係碗到唔理 <br />\n佢又啤住你好似expect你即場食左佢然後大叫「好好味啊！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁啱有大陸親戚一齊食飯 佢老味夠膽夾小龍蝦比我放落碗飯到 搞到成碗飯都係d汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話咩「好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港冇得食點點點」<br />\n<br />\n我即刻夾走舊垃圾 不走半碗飯 再拎過對筷子<br />\n佢塊面黑撚過墨斗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4966b8aa46098acddc1dd5a67d2157c9c65d7c44","tid":1007290,"uid":176169,"like":8,"dislike":32,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"人地一番心意姐 又唔係叫你成日食 <br />\n間中食一兩下比下面人都好啊"},{"pid":"692d0c20fe6d88b15db90832a669603a8666dc3a","tid":1007290,"uid":189480,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主咁唔中意一圍人食飯咪唔好出現 總好過你咁高姿態落人面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d13592c402b8e8b0e85bfbb59055e833fd1b1f","tid":1007290,"uid":41314,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"692d0c20fe6d88b15db90832a669603a8666dc3a","tid":1007290,"uid":189480,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓